msg: Now the checksum of portlet.xml, jetspeed-portlet.xml *and* web.xml will be calculated and checked when a
portlet application is (re)started to see if a full (re)registration might be needed.
Note: this change will lead to re-registering of *all* deployed portlet applications as the current stored
checksum (only taking portlet.xml into account) won't be valid anymore!
